ss]]\n| ''[[Water Lilies (film)|Water Lilies]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=Crash/>\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2012\n| [[Berlin International Film Festival]]\n|[[Shooting Stars Award]]\n|{{n/a}}\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| [[17th Lumi\u00e8res Awards|Lumi\u00e8res Awards]]\n|[[Lumi\u00e8res Award for Most Promising Actress|Most Promising Actress]]\n| rowspan=2|''[[House of Tolerance]]''\n| {{won}}\n| <ref name=Lumiere2012/>\n|-\n| [[37th C\u00e9sar Awards|C\u00e9sar Awards]]\n|[[C\u00e9sar Award for Most Promising Actress|Most Promising Actress]]\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=Cesar2012/>\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2014\n| [[39th C\u00e9sar Awards|C\u00e9sar Awards]]\n|[[C\u00e9sar Award for Best Supporting Actress|Best Supporting Actress]]\n| ''[[Suzanne (2013 film)|Suzanne]]''\n| {{won}}\n| <ref name=Cesar2014/>\n|-\n| [[Prix Suzanne Bianchetti]]\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{n/a}}\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=6|2015\n| [[40th C\u00e9sar Awards|C\u00e9sar Awards]]\n| [[C\u00e9sar Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| rowspan=3|''[[Love at First Fight (film)|Love at First Fight]]''\n| {{won}}\n| <ref name=Cesar2015/>\n|-\n| [[Cairo International Film Festival]]\n| Best Actress\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2|[[20th Lumi\u00e8res Awards|Lumi\u00e8res Awards]]\n| [[Lumi\u00e8res Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=Lumiere2015/>\n|-\n|[[Lumi\u00e8res Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| ''[[In the Name of My Daughter]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=Lumiere2015/>\n|-\n| [[Prix Romy Schneider]]\n|{{n/a}}\n|{{n/a}}\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Globes de Cristal Awards]]\n| [[Globe de Cristal Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| ''[[Love at First Fight (film)|Love at First Fight]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| 2016\n| [[Festival International du Film Francophone de Namur]]\n|Best Actress\n| ''[[Orphan (2016 film)|Orphan]]''\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| [[43rd C\u00e9sar Awards|C\u00e9sar Awards]]\n| [[C\u00e9sar Award for Best Supporting Actress|Best Supporting Actress]]\n| ''[[BPM (Beats per Minute)]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=Cesar2018/>\n|-\n| rowspan=6| 2019\n| [[44th C\u00e9sar Awards|C\u00e9sar Awards]]\n| [[C\u00e9sar Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| rowspan=2| ''[[The Trouble with You]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Globe de Cristal Awards]]\n| [[Globe de Cristal Award for Best Actress|Best Actress - Comedy]]\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| [[32nd European Film Awards|European Film Awards]]\n| [[European Film Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| rowspan=5| ''[[Portrait of a Lady on Fire]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[IndieWire Critics Poll]]\n| Best Actress\n| {{no|10th Place}}\n| align=\"center\" rowspan=\"2\" |<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/best-movies-2019-critics-survey-poll-performances-parasite-adam-driver-lupita-nyongo-1202197615/|title=2019 Critics Poll: The Best Films and Performances According to Over 300 Critics From Around the World|last=Kohn|first=Eric|date=16 December 2019|website=[[IndieWire]]|url-status=live|accessdate=12 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actress\n| {{no|13th Place}}\n|-\n| [[Austin Film Critics Association]]\n| Best Supporting Actress\n| {{nom}}\n| align=\"center\" |<ref>{{cite web|url=https://austinfilmcritics.org/2019-awards-d2faafe15279|title=2019 Awards|last=Stoddard|first=Elizabeth|date=7 January 2020|website=[[Austin Film Critics Association]]|url-status=live|accessdate=12 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2020\n| [[45th C\u00e9sar Awards|C\u00e9sar Awards]]\n| [[C\u00e9sar Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref name=Cesar2020Nom/>\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Ad\u00e8le Haenel}}\n*{{IMDb name|1194748}}\n{{Navboxes\n|title = Awards for Ad\u00e8le Haenel\n|list =\n{{C\u00e9sar Award for Best Actress}}\n{{C\u00e9sar Award for Best Supporting Actress}}\n{{Lumi\u00e8res Award for Most Promising Actress}}\n{{Prix Suzanne Bianchetti}}\n}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Haenel, Adele}}\n[[Category:1989 births